  [PASS] Dealer AI — hits on ≤16, stands on ≥17
    Evidence: Dealer.shouldHit() (Dealer.java:28-39)
    `if (score < 17) return true`. Configurable soft-17 rule via
    `hitsSoft17` flag read from XML config. DealerPlayTask calls
    dealer.shouldHit() correctly in its draw loop.

  [PASS] Hand value calculation (Ace as 1 or 11)
    Evidence: Hand.calculateScore() (Hand.java:46-63), Rank.ACE = 11
