    GameServer.broadcastStateToAll() (GameServer.java:175-179)
    First card shown, remaining cards replaced with face-down ACE/SPADES
    placeholders. Visibility bypass only during SHOWDOWN/ROUND_OVER.
    This IS enforced in the network path. NOTE: GameController.updateCards()
    for local MP mode does NOT hide cards, but GameController.initMultiplayer()
